messages.message: Hey all! I’m planning to do an Instabase architecture overview session this coming Monday (12:30pm PST), mostly for our new engineering hires. It’ll be fairly informal. I’ll do a high level walk-through of the product to our codebase and go wherever questions take us. If anyone else is interested, let me know and I can invite. Would highly recommend having your local dev environment set up so you have an idea of what our codebase looks like already.
@Heymian non eng but I'd love to sit in! Thanks :blush:
